headline: ONEOK Schedules 2025 Annual Meeting of Shareholders; Sets Record Date
summary: ONEOK, Inc. (NYSE: OKE) will hold its 2025 annual meeting of shareholders at 9 a.m. Central Time on May 21, 2025, as a virtual meeting only. The meeting will be accessible through a live webcast.
